      <h1 class="section-header"><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> About CollegePedia</h1>
      <p>
        CollegePedia is a comprehensive online platform dedicated to empowering students, educators, and institutions by providing detailed, reliable, and up-to-date information about colleges and universities worldwide. Founded in 2023, our mission is to simplify the college selection process by offering a one-stop resource for exploring academic programs, campus facilities, and institutional details.
      </p>
      <p>
        Whether you're a prospective student seeking the perfect college, an institution looking to showcase your offerings, or an educator aiming to connect with academic opportunities, CollegePedia is designed to bridge the gap between aspiration and achievement. Our user-friendly interface and robust database make it easy to navigate the complex world of higher education.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="content-card">
      <h2 class="section-header"><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i> Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        At CollegePedia, our mission is to democratize access to higher education information. We strive to provide accurate, transparent, and comprehensive data about colleges, courses, and career paths to help students make informed decisions about their future. We aim to empower every individual with the knowledge they need to pursue their academic and professional goals.
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
        <li>Enable students to find institutions that align with their academic and personal aspirations.</li>
        <li>Support colleges in showcasing their unique strengths and programs.</li>
        <li>Foster a global community of learners and educators through accessible information.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="content-card">
      <h2 class="section-header"><i class="fas fa-eye"></i> Our Vision</h2>
      <p>
        We envision a world where every student has the tools and information to choose the right educational path without barriers. CollegePedia aims to be the leading global platform for higher education exploration, connecting students, institutions, and educators in a seamless ecosystem. By leveraging technology and community-driven insights, we aspire to transform the way people discover and engage with academic opportunities.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="content-card">
